1:1 COMMENT "# nullbody.z - Bare `null` clause bodies"
1:41 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# A match arm, match else, if body, or if else written as the bare"
3:67 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# identifier `null` declares an empty body: nothing runs on that path."
4:71 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# A match/if containing a null (or `{}`) body yields no value, so it can"
5:73 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# only stand as a statement -- consuming it as a value is a compile error."
6:75 EOL "\n"
